    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in exceptional mint condition and represents one of the finest examples you'll find on the used car market. The engine runs flawlessly, starts immediately, and delivers smooth, powerful performance with no hesitation, knocking, or unusual sounds. The transmission shifts crisply and precisely through all gears, and all mechanical systems \u2014 brakes, suspension, cooling, and electrical \u2014 are functioning perfectly. The exterior paint retains a deep, showroom-quality shine with no scratches, dents, or rust, and all trim pieces are intact and pristine. The interior is equally impressive, with no tears, stains, or wear on the seats, carpets, or dashboard, and all controls, gauges, and infotainment features work exactly as intended. This car has been meticulously maintained and is ready for immediate, worry-free driving \u2014 ideal for a buyer who wants the confidence of near-new quality at a used car price.",
      "price": 47000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude98 Dependable & Ready to Roll \u2014 An Honest Fair-Condition Find! This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it gets the job done reliably for everyday driving, and we want to be upfront that it does show its age with some cosmetic wear and minor imperfections you'd expect from a well-used car. The mechanicals are solid and it's fully roadworthy, making it a smart, budget-conscious choice for drivers who prioritize function over flash. If you're looking for affordable, honest transportation without any surprises, this one's worth a look!",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 \u2728 **Pristine Mint Condition \u2014 A Rare Find You'll Love!** Opportunities like this don't come around often! This car is in absolutely mint condition \u2014 we're talking flawless inside and out, with everything working exactly as it should. No dings, no wear, no surprises \u2014 just a beautifully maintained vehicle that's ready to impress from day one. Whether you're looking for a head-turner or simply want the peace of mind that comes with a top-tier used car, this one checks every box. Come see it for yourself \u2014 you won't be disappointed! \ud83c\udf1f",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition \u2014 buyers should approach with full awareness of its current state. The exterior shows significant wear, including deep scratches, dents, rust spots, and faded or peeling paint in multiple areas. The interior is similarly worn, with torn or heavily stained upholstery, damaged trim pieces, and a general sense of long, hard use. Mechanically, the car runs but has known issues that will require attention \u2014 expect to budget for repairs, and a pre-purchase inspection by a trusted mechanic is strongly recommended. This listing is priced accordingly for a buyer who understands they are taking on a project or a vehicle needing substantial work. No surprises here \u2014 what you see is what you get.",
      "price": 6500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Here's a solid, dependable vehicle that's ready to impress. This well-maintained car presents beautifully, with a clean interior and exterior that reflect careful ownership. All major systems are in strong working order, and it drives with the confidence you'd expect from a quality pre-owned vehicle. Whether you're commuting daily or hitting the open road on weekends, this car delivers reliability and comfort without the new-car price tag. Priced fairly and honestly \u2014 come see it for yourself and experience the difference.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, car lovers! \ud83d\ude97 I've got a fantastic ride here that I'm genuinely excited to pass along to its next happy owner. This beauty is in solid good condition \u2014 she's been well cared for, drives smoothly, and is ready to hit the road without missing a beat. Sure, she's got a little character from her years on the road (what well-loved car doesn't?), but nothing that gets in the way of a great driving experience. The interior is comfortable and clean, the mechanicals are sound, and she starts right up every single time. I'm a straight shooter \u2014 what you see is what you get, and I think you're going to love what you see! Come take her for a spin and feel the difference yourself. Priced to make you smile and move quickly, so don't wait too long!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a seriously sorted driver that delivers exactly what enthusiasts demand. This machine rides on a well-maintained suspension geometry with responsive steering feel intact \u2014 no slop, no vagueness. The powertrain exhibits strong compression across all cylinders, with smooth throttle response and a transmission that shifts crisply through the gate. Braking hardware is in solid working order, offering confident pedal feel and straight-line stopping authority. The exterior carries honest road character with minor cosmetic blemishes consistent with a car that's been driven, not babied \u2014 but structurally clean with no compromised panels. Interior ergonomics remain fully functional, with all primary controls operating as intended. Service history reflects attentive ownership. This is a car that rewards a driver who appreciates mechanical integrity over showroom gloss. Ready to perform on your first drive.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    }
  ],
